## P1

```elixir
defmodule P1 do
  def solve(n), do: recur(n, 1, 1)

  defp recur(1, h, _) do
    h
  end

  defp recur(n, h, r) when rem(n, 2) == 1 do
    recur(div(n, 2), h + 2 ** r, r + 1)
  end

  defp recur(n, h, r) when rem(n, 2) == 0 do
    recur(div(n, 2), h, r + 1)
  end
end
```

```elixir
P1.solve(live)
```

